01:28:48,290 --> 01:28:50,170
Zhao Liang threaten Xiao Ma in sign language before session.

1115
01:28:50,170 --> 01:28:50,790
You're lying.
I didn't.

1116
01:28:52,000 --> 01:28:52,630
Stop. Don't move.

1117
01:28:52,790 --> 01:28:53,790
I want to report it.

1118
01:28:53,790 --> 01:28:55,170
There are two more of Zhao Liang's people

1119
01:28:55,750 --> 01:28:57,000
in the fifth row.

1120
01:29:15,170 --> 01:29:17,290
Mumu is safe.

1121
01:29:17,290 --> 01:29:20,080
Don't be so silly anymore.

1122
01:29:36,710 --> 01:29:38,960
Court proceedings will now resume.

1123
01:29:41,330 --> 01:29:42,290
Do you have any objections

1124
01:29:42,290 --> 01:29:44,330
to the defendant Li Mei's statement?

1125
01:29:47,080 --> 01:29:48,080
No.

1126
01:29:48,790 --> 01:29:50,790
Has Zhao Liang ever threatened you?

1127
01:29:55,580 --> 01:29:56,580
Yes.

1128
01:29:57,330 --> 01:30:00,170
Do you know that what you did was a crime?

1129
01:30:05,540 --> 01:30:06,670
Yes.

1130
01:30:07,710 --> 01:30:09,960
Do you have any additional statements?

1131
01:30:19,210 --> 01:30:20,330
I committed a crime.

1132
01:30:21,750 --> 01:30:24,670
I'm sorry. I did wrong.

1133
01:30:29,460 --> 01:30:30,710
I am deaf.

1134
01:30:33,420 --> 01:30:35,500
I have a kind daughter.

1135
01:30:38,420 --> 01:30:39,670
I work hard

1136
01:30:41,500 --> 01:30:44,580
to give Mumu the best life.

1137
01:30:45,420 --> 01:30:47,790
But it's really hard.

1138
01:30:49,420 --> 01:30:51,920
I can only smile at others,

1139
01:30:53,580 --> 01:30:56,210
but others don't understand me.

1140
01:31:00,790 --> 01:31:03,170
Fortunately, Mumu can translate for me.

1141
01:31:07,330 --> 01:31:08,580
I thought

1142
01:31:10,710 --> 01:31:13,210
that as long as we hid in our own world, it would be enough.

1143
01:31:15,210 --> 01:31:17,790
But her mom wanted to take Mumu abroad.

1144
01:31:19,210 --> 01:31:20,210
I scared.

1145
01:31:22,580 --> 01:31:24,790
I was afraid I'll never see Mumu again.

1146
01:31:27,330 --> 01:31:30,170
But I shouldn't have kept her by my side

1147
01:31:30,460 --> 01:31:31,710
to be my ears.

1148
01:31:33,420 --> 01:31:35,040
I was too selfish.

1149
01:31:39,040 --> 01:31:43,540
Mumu, you have to be yourself and grow up well.

1150
01:31:49,540 --> 01:31:51,830
I don't deserve to be your father.

1151
01:31:57,290 --> 01:31:58,790
I've been thinking lately

1152
01:32:00,540 --> 01:32:02,290
why I can't hear

1153
01:32:05,290 --> 01:32:07,670
and why I can't speak.

1154
01:32:11,000 --> 01:32:13,750
I really want to hear your voice.

1155
01:32:18,460 --> 01:32:19,880
Your voice

1156
01:32:19,880 --> 01:32:24,880
must be the best sound in the world.

1157
01:32:33,420 --> 01:32:35,080
Sounds

1158
01:32:36,790 --> 01:32:38,420
good.

1159
01:32:41,170 --> 01:32:42,790
Sounds

1160
01:32:45,420 --> 01:32:47,040
good.

1161
01:33:21,920 --> 01:33:23,080
Li Mei's testimony

1162
01:33:23,250 --> 01:33:25,670
helped reduce Ma's sentence a lot.

1163
01:33:26,670 --> 01:33:29,920
But the case involved too much money.

1164
01:33:30,790 --> 01:33:33,420
In the end, he was sentenced to six years.

1165
01:33:38,790 --> 01:33:41,420
I know it's tough for deaf people to be heard,

1166
01:33:42,290 --> 01:33:46,290
but deaf people should have a fair trial.

1167
01:33:52,380 --> 01:33:53,420
Believe me,

1168
01:33:54,170 --> 01:33:56,170
I will help your voices be heard.

1169
01:33:56,540 --> 01:33:57,710
Okay?

1170
01:34:15,920 --> 01:34:17,790
Secretly recorded videos can also be used as evidence?

1171
01:34:18,170 --> 01:34:20,380
Her WeChat chat records can be evidence.

1172
01:34:20,790 --> 01:34:22,170
But you forced her to delete them.

1173
01:34:22,290 --> 01:34:23,540
Don't talk nonsense.

1174
01:34:23,960 --> 01:34:24,670
What chat evidence?

1175
01:34:25,380 --> 01:34:26,670
Can the data be recovered?

1176
01:34:26,790 --> 01:34:27,790
It should be no problem.

1177
01:34:28,130 --> 01:34:29,580
The technicians are working on it.

1178
01:34:30,290 --> 01:34:30,790
Officer,

1179
01:34:30,960 --> 01:34:33,290
I felt sorry for her, so I gave her this job.

1180
01:34:33,670 --> 01:34:34,670
I also sympathize with her,

1181
01:34:34,670 --> 01:34:36,210
which is why I care about her.

1182
01:34:36,330 --> 01:34:38,710
You are three months behind on her salary.

1183
01:34:38,790 --> 01:34:39,920
That's a fact, right?

1184
01:34:40,330 --> 01:34:41,290
She suddenly wants to leave.
She was doing a good job.

1185
01:34:42,210 --> 01:34:43,170
Why would she leave?

1186
01:34:43,290 --> 01:34:44,420
I think these deaf-mutes

1187
01:34:44,460 --> 01:34:45,630
must be missing something in their brains.

1188
01:34:45,960 --> 01:34:46,920
Watch your attitude.

1189
01:34:46,920 --> 01:34:48,170
They're not deaf-mutes.

1190
01:34:49,830 --> 01:34:51,290
They just can't hear,

1191
01:34:51,290 --> 01:34:52,290
they're not mute.

1192
01:34:52,710 --> 01:34:53,210
Please call

1193
01:34:53,210 --> 01:34:55,540
them deaf or hearing-impaired.

1194
01:34:57,670 --> 01:34:59,040
And do you really understand deaf people?

1195
01:35:00,580 --> 01:35:01,960
Do you know how afraid they are of our world

1196
01:35:01,960 --> 01:35:03,830
because they can't hear?

1197
01:35:05,960 --> 01:35:08,790
Your behavior is exactly what she's afraid of.

1198
01:35:09,040 --> 01:35:10,290
Let's get this straight.

1199
01:35:10,540 --> 01:35:11,920
I'm not the criminal.

1200
01:35:12,170 --> 01:35:13,290
She's the criminal.

1201
01:35:14,540 --> 01:35:17,460
We wake up every day, go out, eat, go to work,

1202
01:35:17,540 --> 01:35:18,670
ask the boss for our salary,

1203
01:35:18,670 --> 01:35:19,920
protect ourselves from harm

1204
01:35:19,920 --> 01:35:20,670
and being insulted.

1205
01:35:21,290 --> 01:35:23,920
These are the most basic things for a normal person.

1206
01:35:25,670 --> 01:35:27,290
But did you know that for a deaf person,

1207
01:35:27,880 --> 01:35:29,040
they need to put in a hundred

1208
01:35:29,040 --> 01:35:30,170
or a thousand times more effort

1209
01:35:30,170 --> 01:35:31,790
and may still fall short.

1210
01:35:32,420 --> 01:35:34,330
Just to get up every day and face the world,

1211
01:35:34,330 --> 01:35:36,040
they have to muster a lot of courage.

1212
01:35:36,420 --> 01:35:37,580
When they encounter problems,

1213
01:35:37,670 --> 01:35:39,670
they may even feel abandoned

1214
01:35:39,670 --> 01:35:40,670
and excluded by society.

1215
01:35:42,670 --> 01:35:44,170
So deaf people are very patient.

1216
01:35:45,790 --> 01:35:47,710
You are the one who pushed such a patient girl

1217
01:35:47,960 --> 01:35:49,080
to the police station.

1218
01:35:49,830 --> 01:35:51,670
You even tried to land her in prison.

1219
01:35:52,290 --> 01:35:53,420
Can you live with yourself?

1220
01:35:54,170 --> 01:35:55,250
We are now going to question you

1221
01:35:55,250 --> 01:35:57,580
about the harassment.

1222
01:35:58,130 --> 01:35:59,000
Please cooperate.

1223
01:36:04,790 --> 01:36:06,670
I will notify you as soon as I have any news.

1224
01:36:07,290 --> 01:36:08,170
Please do.

1225
01:36:09,920 --> 01:36:11,290
You haven't told me yet,

1226
01:36:11,290 --> 01:36:13,460
how can I recognize a deaf person at a glance?

1227
01:36:16,040 --> 01:36:17,460
When you walk into a place,

1228
01:36:17,920 --> 01:36:19,710
deaf people will smile at you

1229
01:36:20,170 --> 01:36:21,170
the first moment they see you.

1230
01:36:28,830 --> 01:36:33,630
Heichuan: Social media influencer, loves sharing his life. Dreams of buying a house for his wife.

1231
01:36:34,380 --> 01:36:38,920
Fu Yan: Nickname "Hippo," born deaf. Can do electrical work, has set up street stalls, and has a humorous personality.

1232
01:36:40,250 --> 01:36:44,580
Liao Tianxin: Enjoys playing games and eating hotpot with friends.

1233
01:36:46,290 --> 01:36:49,960
Du Yinling: Senior sign language educator, program host. Deaf culture blogger, dedicated to promoting sign language education.

1234
01:36:49,960 --> 01:36:53,080
Leona: Became deaf due to a fever as a child, dreams of being an actress.

1235
01:36:54,750 --> 01:36:58,960
Gu Jirong: Retired worker from Chongqing High Voltage Switchgear Factory. Loves photography and traveling.

1236
01:37:00,460 --> 01:37:05,000
Yuan Ying: Currently a dancer in the Sichuan Disabled Art Troupe, winner of the National Disabled People's Art Festival Gold Award.

1237
01:37:06,500 --> 01:37:08,830
Feng Wen: Delivery person, part-time barista.

1238
01:37:08,830 --> 01:37:11,040
Li Bo: Would most want to be a soldier if he wasn't deaf.

1239
01:37:11,040 --> 01:37:13,380
Wang Xianhe: Former dancer in the China Disabled People's Performing Art Troupe.

1240
01:37:15,750 --> 01:37:17,460
Xiao Yongliao: Former typesetter in a printing factory.

1241
01:37:17,460 --> 01:37:19,210
Zeng Ying: Dreams of communicating smoothly with people who don't know sign language.

1242
01:37:19,210 --> 01:37:20,830
Huang Jiyue: Loves doing charity work, volunteer for the Deaf Knife Sharpening Team.

1243
01:37:20,830 --> 01:37:22,540
Tang Xinghua: Often helps deaf people in need.

1244
01:37:22,540 --> 01:37:24,330
Niu Dangying: The sound she most wants to hear is her son calling her "Mom."

1245
01:37:25,580 --> 01:37:27,670
Xu Houlan: If she could hear, she would want to be a singer.

1246
01:37:27,670 --> 01:37:29,790
Li Jian: Former storekeeper at a pharmaceutical company, has a cute granddaughter.

1247
01:37:29,790 --> 01:37:32,080
Wang Xuemei: Has a son and daughter, both hearing.

1248
01:37:34,080 --> 01:37:38,830
Hou Liang and Wang Dan: Married for five years, run coffee shops together in Shanghai.
They dream of one day being able to drive around the world.

1249
01:37:53,540 --> 01:38:07,080
After being released from prison, Xiao Ma ran a housekeeping company with his deaf friends and lived a peaceful and stable life.
