to engage in public welfare sign language translation work, dedicated to speaking out for more deaf people.

1250
01:38:08,630 --> 01:38:15,000
The little girl who once wanted to protect her father can now protect more people.

1251
01:38:15,670 --> 01:38:24,170
The world can be silent, but they will always have love.
